\c 16
\s Ukungathembeki kweJerusalema
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kimi futhi lisithi:
\v 2 Ndodana yomuntu, yenza iJerusalema yazi amanyala ayo\x + 22.2,26. 43.11. 20.4,11.\x*,
\v 3 uthi: Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova kuyo iJerusalema: Ukudabuka kwakho lokuzalwa kwakho\x + 21.30.\x* kungokwelizwe lamaKhanani\x + 15.29,56. Hos. 12.7.\x*; uyihlo\x + 15.45.\x* wayengumAmori\x + Gen. 15.16.\x* lonyoko\x + 16.45.\x* umHethi\x + Hlu. 1.26.\x*.
\v 4 Mayelana lokuzalwa kwakho, ngosuku owazalwa ngalo inkaba yakho kayiqunywanga, njalo kawugeziswanga emanzini ukuthi \add u\add*hlanjululwe, kawugcotshwanga ngetshwayi ngitsho, kawugoqelwanga ngamalembu ngitsho\x + Hos. 2.3.\x*.
\v 5 Kakulalihlo elakuhawukelayo, ukuthi lenze yiloba yikuphi kwalezizinto kuwe, ukuthi likuhawukele\x + 5.11.\x*. Kodwa waphoselwa ebusweni bendle, ekunengekeni kobuntu bakho\x + 16.45.\x*, ngosuku owazalwa ngalo\x + Hos. 2.3.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Kwathi ngisedlula kuwe ngikubona uqhatsha egazini lakho, ngathi kuwe usegazini lakho\x + 16.22. 19.10.\x*: Phila; yebo ngathi kuwe usegazini lakho: Phila\x + 16.22. 19.10.\x*.
\v 7 Ngikwenzile waba linani elikhulu, waba njengehlumela leganga, wanda, wakhula\x + Eks. 1.7.\x*, wafika emicecisweni emihle\x + 16.11,13.\x*; amabele \add akho\add* abumbekile, lenwele zakho zakhula; kanti wawunqunu uze\x + 16.22,39. 23.29.\x*.
\v 8 Kwathi ngisedlula kuwe ngakubona, khangela-ke, isikhathi sakho sasiyisikhathi sothando; ngasengisendlala umphetho wesembatho sami phezu kwakho, ngembesa ubunqunu bakho; yebo, ngafunga kuwe, ngangena esivumelwaneni lawe, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + 5.3. Ruthe 3.9. Jer. 2.2.\x*, wasusiba ngowami\x + Eks. 19.5.\x*.
\v 9 Ngasengikugezisa ngamanzi, ngahlambulula igazi lakho elinengi kuwe, ngakugcoba ngamafutha\x + Ruthe 3.3. Hlab. 23.5.\x*.
\v 10 Ngakugqokisa ilembu elifekethisiweyo\x + 16.13,18. 17.3. 26.16. 27.7,16,24. Eks. 26.36. 27.16. 28.39.\x*, ngakufaka amanyathela\x + Luka 15.22.\x* ezikhumba zikamantswane\x + Eks. 25.5. 26.14.\x*, ngakubhincisa ilembu elicolekileyo kakhulu\x + 16.13. 27.7. Gen. 41.42. Isam. 19.8.\x*, ngakwembesa ngesilika\x + 16.13.\x*.
\v 11 Ngakucecisa ngeziceciso\x + 23.40. 16.7,13. Isa. 61.10.\x*, ngafaka amasongo ezandleni zakho\x + 23.42. Gen. 24.22,30,47. Nani 31.50.\x*, leketane\x + Gen. 41.42.\x* entanyeni yakho\x + Zaga 1.9.\x*.
\v 12 Ngafaka isongo emakhaleni akho, lamacici ezindlebeni zakho\x + Nani 31.50.\x*, lomqhele omuhle ekhanda lakho\x + 23.42. Esta 2.17.\x*.
\v 13 Ngokunjalo waceciswa ngegolide lesiliva\x + 16.11.\x*, lesembatho sakho sasingeselembu elicolekileyo kakhulu\x + 16.10.\x*, lesilika\x + 16.10.\x*, lelembu elifekethisiweyo\x + 16.10.\x*; wadla impuphu ecolekileyo, loluju, lamafutha\x + 16.19. Dute. 32.13,14.\x*; waba muhle kakhulukazi, waphumelela waba ngumbuso\x + 16.13,15,25. Hlab. 48.2.\x*.
\v 14 Lodumo lwakho lwaphumela ezizweni\x + 23.10. Lilo 2.15.\x* ngobuhle bakho\x + 16.13,15,25. Hlab. 48.2.\x*\x + 23.10. Lilo 2.15.\x*, ngoba babuphelele ngenkazimulo yami, engayibeka phezu kwakho, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + 27.10.\x*.
