\v 15 Kodwa wathembela ebuhleni bakho\x + 16.13,15,25. Hlab. 48.2.\x*, wawula ngenxa yebizo lakho\x + 16.16,17,26,28,29. 23.3,8,11,12. Levi 17.7. Isa. 1.21. 57.8. Jer. 2.20. 3.2,6,20. Hos. 1.2. Eks. 34.15. Hlab. 73.27.\x*, wathululela ukuwula kwakho kuye wonke odlulayo\x + 16.25.\x*, kwaba ngokwakhe.
\v 16 Wathatha ezembathweni zakho, wazenzela indawo eziphakemeyo\x + 2 Kho. 23.7.\x* ngemibala\x + Gen. 30.32,33,35,39.\x*, wawulela phezu kwazo\x + 16.16,17,26,28,29. 23.3,8,11,12. Levi 17.7. Isa. 1.21. 57.8. Jer. 2.20. 3.2,6,20. Hos. 1.2. Eks. 34.15. Hlab. 73.27.\x*; \add izinto ezinje\add* kaziyikuza, njalo kakuyikwenzeka.
\v 17 Wathatha futhi izitsha zakho ezinhle egolideni lami lesiliveni sami engangikunike khona\x + 16.13.\x*, wazenzela izithombe zabesilisa\x + 7.20. 23.14.\x*, wawula lazo\x + 16.16,17,26,28,29. 23.3,8,11,12. Levi 17.7. Isa. 1.21. 57.8. Jer. 2.20. 3.2,6,20. Hos. 1.2. Eks. 34.15. Hlab. 73.27.\x*.
\v 18 Wathatha izembatho zakho ezifekethisiweyo\x + 16.10.\x*, wazisibekela; wabeka amafutha ami lempepha yami phambi kwazo\x + 23.41.\x*.
\v 19 Lokudla kwami engakunika khona\x + Hos. 2.8.\x*, impuphu ecolekileyo lamafutha loluju \add e\add*ngangikondla \add ngakho\x + 16.19. Dute. 32.13,14.\x*\add*, wakubeka phambi kwazo kwaba liphunga elimnandi; kwaba njalo, itsho iNkosi uJehova.
