\v 20 Wasuthatha amadodana akho lamadodakazi akho, owawungizalele wona\x + 16.21,36. 23.37.\x*, wawahlabela zona ukuze adliwe\x + 16.36. 20.26,31. 23.37. Isa. 57.5. Jer. 7.31.\x*. Ukuphinga kwakho kwakukuncinyane yini\x + 34.18. Nani 16.9.\x*,
\v 21 ukuze ubulale abantwana bami\x + 16.21,36. 23.37.\x*, ubanikela ukuba ubadabulise\x + 16.36. 20.26,31. 23.37. Isa. 57.5. Jer. 7.31.\x* \add emlilweni\add* kuzo\x + 20.31.\x*?
\v 22 Lakuwo wonke amanyala akho lokuwula kwakho kawukhumbulanga insuku zobutsha bakho\x + 16.8,43,60. 23.3,8,19. Jer. 2.2. Hlab. 129.1.\x*, lapho wawunqunu uze\x + 16.7.\x*, uqhatsha\x + 16.6.\x* egazini lakho\x + 16.22. 19.10.\x*.
