\v 23 Kwasekusithi emva kwayo yonke inkohlakalo yakho (maye, maye kuwe! itsho iNkosi uJehova),
\v 24 wazakhela idundulu, wazenzela indawo ephakemeyo kuso sonke isitalada\x + 16.31. Isa. 57.7. Jer. 2.20. 3.2.\x*.
\v 25 Kuyo yonke inhloko yendlela wakhile indawo yakho ephakemeyo\x + 16.31. 21.19. 42.12. 21.21. Lilo 2.19. Zaga 9.14. Jer. 3.2.\x*, wenza ubuhle bakho banengeka\x + 16.13,15,25. Hlab. 48.2.\x*, wavulela bonke abedlulayo izinyawo zakho\x + 16.15.\x*, wandisa ukuwula kwakho\x + 16.26,29. 23.19. Jer. 11.15.\x*.
\v 26 Njalo waphinga\x + 16.15.\x* labantwana bamaGibhithe, omakhelwane bakho\x + 20.7,8. 23.19-21. 8.10.\x*, abakhulu ngenyama, wandisa ukuwula kwakho\x + 16.26,29. 23.19. Jer. 11.15.\x*, ukuze ungithukuthelise\x + Jer. 7.18.\x*.
\v 27 Ngakho, khangela, ngelulele isandla sami phezu kwakho, nganciphisa\x + 5.11.\x* isabelo sakho esimisiweyo\x + Jobe 23.12.\x*, ngakunikela entandweni yabakuzondayo\x + 16.37.\x*, amadodakazi amaFilisti, alenhloni ngendlela yakho embi\x + 16.57.\x*.
\v 28 Uwulile futhi\x + 16.15.\x* labantwana bamaAsiriya ngoba ungasuthiseki; yebo, uwulile lawo, kube kanti kawusuthisekanga\x + 23.12. 2 Kho. 16.7-18. 2 Lan. 28.16-21. Jer. 2.18,36.\x*.
\v 29 Wandisa futhi ukuwula kwakho\x + 16.15.\x*\x + 16.26,29. 23,19. Jer. 11.15.\x* elizweni leKanani\x + 16.3.\x* kuze kube seKhaladiya\x + 23.14-16.\x*; kodwa langalokhu kawusuthisekanga.
\v 30 Ibuthakathaka kangakanani inhliziyo yakho, itsho iNkosi uJehova, ekwenzeni kwakho zonke lezizinto, umsebenzi wowesifazana ophingayo, obusayo,
\v 31 ekwakheni kwakho idundulu lakho enhlokweni yayo yonke indlela\x + 16.25.\x*, wenza indawo yakho ephakemeyo kuso sonke isitalada\x + 16.24.\x*, kanti kawubanga njengewule ngoba wadelela iholo lewule\x + 16.33,34,36.\x*.
\v 32 Umfazi ofebayo, endaweni yendoda yakhe uthatha abemzini\x + 23.5. Nani 5.19.\x*!
\v 33 Bapha isipho kuwo wonke amawule. Kodwa wena unika isipho sakho kuzo zonke izithandwa zakho, uzithenga ukuze zize kuwe enhlangothini zonke ngokuwula kwakho\x + 16.33,34,36.\x*\x + 16.34,41. Hos. 8.9.\x*.
\v 34 Ngakho kuwe kulokuphambene labesifazana ekuwuleni kwakho, ngoba kakho olandela wena ukuyawula; lekunikeni kwakho iholo lewule\x + 16.34,41. Hos. 8.9.\x*, njalo unganikwanga iholo lewule, ngakho usube ngophambeneyo\x + 16.33,34,36.\x*.
