\v 35 Ngakho, wena wule, zwana ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 36 Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Ngoba ukuwula kwakho kuthululiwe, lobunqunu bakho bembulwa ngokuwula kwakho lezithandwa zakho, langazo zonke izithombe zezinengiso zakho\x + 24.11. 16.34,41 .\x*, langegazi labantwana bakho\x + 16.20,21,38. Jer. 2.34.\x* owazinika bona\x + 16.20,21,38. Jer. 2.34.\x*.
\v 37 Ngakho, khangela, ngizaqoqa zonke izithandwa zakho obuthokoza lazo\x + 23.22. Hos. 8.10.\x*, lazo zonke obuzithanda kanye lazo zonke obuzizonda\x + 23.28. 16.27.\x*; ngiziqoqe zimelane lawe zivela enhlangothini zonke\x + 23.22. Hos. 8.10.\x*, ngembule ubunqunu bakho kuzo\x + 23.10,29. 16.39. Isam. 17.16. Isa. 3.17. Hos. 2.10.\x* ukuze zibone bonke ubunqunu bakho\x + Lilo 1.8.\x*.
\v 38 Njalo ngizakugweba\x + 21.30.\x* \add nge\add*zahlulelo zabesifazana abafebayo\x + 23.45.\x*\x + Levi 20.10. Dute. 22.22.\x* labachithi begazi\x + 16.20,21,38. Jer. 2.34.\x*\x + 23.45.\x*\x + 18.10. 23.37. 22.3. Gen. 9.6.\x*, ngikuphe igazi lentukuthelo lobukhwele.
\v 39 Ngizakunikela futhi esandleni sazo, ziwisele phansi idundulu lakho\x + 16.24,25.\x*, zidilize indawo zakho eziphakemeyo\x + 16.24,25.\x*, zikuhlubule izigqoko zakho\x + Lilo 1.8.\x*\x + 23.26.\x*\x + Hos. 2.3.\x*, zithathe izinto zakho ezinhle\x + 23.26.\x*, zikutshiye unqunu uze\x + 16.7.\x*.
\v 40 Zikwenyuselele ixuku\x + 23.46. Jobe 11.10.\x*, zikukhande ngamatshe, zikugwaze ngezinkemba zazo\x + 23.47. Joha. 8.5,7.\x*.
\v 41 Zitshise izindlu zakho ngomlilo\x + 23.47. 2 Kho. 25.9. Jer. 39.8. 52.13.\x*, zenze izahlulelo phezu kwakho phambi kwamehlo abesifazana abanengi\x + 5.8.\x*. Njalo ngizakwenza uyekele ekubeni liwule\x + 23.27. 22.15. 23.48.\x*, njalo kawusayikupha iholo lewule futhi\x + 16.33,34.\x*.
\v 42 Ngokunjalo ngizakwenza ukukuthukuthelela kwami kuphumule, lobukhwele bami busuke kuwe; njalo ngizathula, ngingabe ngisathukuthela\x + 5.13.\x*.
\v 43 Ngenxa yokuthi ungakhumbulanga insuku zobutsha bakho\x + 16.22.\x*, kodwa ungithukuthelisile ngazo zonke lezi\add zinto\x + Efe. 4.30.\x*\add*, khangela, mina-ke ngizakwehlisela futhi indlela yakho phezu kwekhanda \add lakho\add*, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + 7.4.\x*. Njalo kawuyikwenza lobububi phezu kwazo zonke izinengiso zakho\x + 22.9.\x*.
