\v 44 Khangela, wonke osebenzisa izaga uzasebenzisa isaga ngawe\x + 17.2. 18.2,3. 20.49. 24.3. Hab. 2.6. Nani 21.27.\x* esithi: Njengonina \add injalo\add* indodakazi yakhe.
\v 45 Wena uyindodakazi kanyoko, owayesenyanya indoda yakhe labantwana bakhe\x + 16.5. Levi 26.30.\x*; lawe ungudade wabodadewenu\x + 16.46,61. 23. 4.\x*, ababesenyanya amadoda abo labantwana babo\x + 16.5. Levi 26.30.\x*; unyoko wayengumHethi\x + 16.3.\x* loyihlo umAmori\x + 16.3.\x*.
\v 46 Lodadewenu omdala yiSamariya\x + 23.2. 16.51,53,55. Jer. 23.13.\x*, yena lamadodakazi akhe abahlala ngakwesokhohlo sakho\x + Isa. 54.3.\x*\x + Gen. 14.15.\x*; lodadewenu omncane kuwe, ohlala ngakwesokunene sakho\x + Isa. 54.3.\x*\x + 10.3. 1 Sam. 23.19.\x*, yiSodoma lamadodakazi ayo\x + 16.48,49,55,56. Isa. 1.10.\x*.
\v 47 Kanti kawuhambanga ngezindlela zabo, wenze njengokwezinengiso zabo\x + 5.7.\x*; kwakunjengento encinyane enengekayo; kodwa wonakala kulabo kuzo zonke izindlela zakho\x + 5.6. 16.48,51,52. 23.11. 2 Kho. 21.9.\x*.
\v 48 Kuphila kwami, itsho iNkosi uJehova\x + Isa. 49.18.\x*, isibili iSodoma udadewenu kayenzanga, yona lamadodakazi ayo, njengokwenza kwakho, wena lamadodakazi akho\x + 16.46. Mat. 10.15. 11.24.\x*.
\v 49 Khangela, lesi sasiyisiphambeko seSodoma udadewenu: Ukuzigqaja, ukusutha isinkwa, lokuchelesa okulokuthula kwakukuyo lakumadodana ayo, kodwa kaqinisanga isandla sabayanga labaswelayo\x + Gen. 13.10.\x*.
\v 50 Babeziphakamisa, benza isinengiso phambi kwami\x + Gen. 13.13. 18.20. 19.5.\x*; ngakho ngabasusa\x + Gen. 19.24.\x* njengokubona kwami\x + Gen 18.21.\x*.
\v 51 Futhi iSamariya kayonanga ngengxenye yezono zakho\x + 16.46,47.\x*; kodwa wena wandisile izinengiso zakho kulabo, walungisisa odadewenu ngezinengiso zakho zonke ozenzileyo\x + 16.52. Jer. 3.11.\x*.
\v 52 Lawe\x + Roma 2.3.\x*, thwala ihlazo lakho\x + 16.54. 32.24.\x*, wena owahlulele odadewenu\x + Hlab. 106.30.\x*, ngezono zakho ozenzileyo ngokunengeka okwedlula bona; balungile kulawe. Ngakho lawe woba lenhloni, uthwale ihlazo lakho\x + 16.46,47.\x*, ngoba ubalungisisile odadewenu\x + 16.52. Jer. 3.11.\x*.
